                                                    <p>HELP USA’s mission is to provide housing and the supportive services necessary for the homeless and people in need to become and remain self-reliant.</p>
                                                    <p>Mentoring USA’s mission is to create sustained and supportive mentor relationships for children ages 7–21 in need. The program matches youth across the country with inspirational adult mentors who can guide them in developing better self-esteem, creating healthy relationships and making positive life choices.</p>
